  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "When sending TrueUSD, the automatic `gasLimit` is incorrect because the `eth_estimateGas` request does not supply the `gasPrice` parameter.\r\n\r\nSmart contracts can condition on `gasPrice` using the `GASPRICE` opcode, `3a`. Not supplying the `gasPrice` parameter leads to incorrect estimates and reverted transactions.\r\n\r\nYou can test this by calculating the gasLimit for a TrueUSD transfer. The automatic gasLimit should be approximately 21k lower for 1 wei than for 40 gwei; instead, it is the same.",
