    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Additionally, you might consider padding your gasLimit. MetaMask pads their estimated gasLimit by 50% to anticipate possible variances. In particular, one SSTORE op can vary in gas by 15k.\r\n\r\nFor example if a non-empty token recipient account were emptied between estimateGas and when your transaction confirmed, that would add 15k to the gas cost.",
